metadata.title: Kindle Fire HD 10 2021 Case, Fire HD 10 Plus Case,REASUN PU Leather Card Slots with Auto Sleep/Wake Case for New Kindle Fire HD 10 & 10 Plus Tablet (11th Generation, 2021 Release) (Space Panda)
features: [Compatible Model] Designed exclusively for Amazon All-New Kindle Fire HD 10 and Fire HD 10 Plus tablet (10.1" Display, 11th Generation, 2021 Release) ,NOT Fit Other Tablet.
[Auto Wake/Sleep Function] Built-in magnetic strip, automatically wakes or puts your tablet to sleep when the lid is opened and closed. Protects and extends battery life.
[Kickstand Feature] Built-in stand with two angles viewing and typing, so you can choose a comfortable way to watch movies, play games and online chatting.

[Premium Material] Synthetic leather exterior, soft microfiber interior and TPU back cover, magnetic connection keeps the cover securely closed while on the go, against water, dust, fingerprint, scratches.
[Precise Cutouts] Proper cutouts ensure the accessibility to all functions of your device without removing the case, such as buttons, cameras and speaker, etc.
description: [Support Auto Sleep/Wake Feature] [Adjustable Angles Stand] [Card Slots Design] [Precise Cutouts].

1:100% Brand New and High Quality Leather Material.Premium PU leather exterior and soft microfiber interior offer great protection against daily use. 2.Design For All-New Kindle Fire HD 10 2021 & Kindle Fire HD 10 Plus Tablet (11th Generation, 2021 Release) Tablet, NOT compatible with any other models. 3.Full Protection: Made of premium durable PU leather and flexible TPU back cover,perfectly fit your tablet,protect your tablet from fingerprints,dirt,drops and scratches. 4.Precise Cutouts: All the ports, buttons and controls are accessible without removing the case. Easy access to speakers, camera, charging ports, earphone jack, etc. 5.Multi-Angle Viewing Stand: Built-in stand for hands-free viewing in landscape orientation. Perfect for reading, typing, watching movies or making video calls. 6.Magnetic Closure Design: Flexible and secure enough to hold it open or shut.With magnetic connection keeps the cover securely closed while on the go. 7.Auto Wake/Sleep Feature: Automatically wakes or puts your device to sleep when the lid is opened and closed.Effectively extend the battery life. 8.Card Slots Design: Interior card slots pocket are designed for carrying your credit card / business cards/ some notes or bills while on the go. Case only, Tablet not included.
